1
00:01:35,200 --> 00:01:36,159
You came because of

2
00:01:36,159 --> 00:01:37,519
those rumors, right?

3
00:01:38,640 --> 00:01:39,799
About us two,

4
00:01:41,159 --> 00:01:42,200
I bet everyone in your household

5
00:01:42,200 --> 00:01:43,040
knows it by now.

6
00:01:44,439 --> 00:01:45,799
Mungkin.

7
00:01:48,840 --> 00:01:50,359
As for who started it,

8
00:01:51,239 --> 00:01:52,239
it's easy to guess.

9
00:01:52,560 --> 00:01:53,680
Can't be more than three people.

10
00:01:54,760 --> 00:01:56,359
For a young lady,

11
00:01:56,799 --> 00:01:57,840
this kind of thing's awkward to handle.

12
00:01:58,319 --> 00:01:58,959
So…

13
00:01:59,719 --> 00:02:00,799
maybe I should step in.

14
00:02:02,640 --> 00:02:03,959
What are you planning to do?

15
00:02:05,200 --> 00:02:06,079
Simple.

16
00:02:07,599 --> 00:02:08,719
I'll come propose.

17
00:02:20,439 --> 00:02:21,080
No,

18
00:02:22,759 --> 00:02:23,879
that's way too fast!

19
00:02:24,080 --> 00:02:26,000
Aren't we still figuring things out?

20
00:02:27,719 --> 00:02:29,159
Please don't do anything yet.

21
00:02:29,280 --> 00:02:30,639
Saya bisa menanganinya sendiri.

22
00:02:31,639 --> 00:02:33,000
Since everyone already knows,

23
00:02:33,000 --> 00:02:33,919
we might as well

24
00:02:34,599 --> 00:02:35,439
make it official.

25
00:02:36,159 --> 00:02:36,680
TIDAK.

26
00:02:38,360 --> 00:02:39,919
I still need time to think.

27
00:02:41,400 --> 00:02:42,599
Please, I'm begging you.

28
00:02:50,400 --> 00:02:50,960
Baiklah.

29
00:02:51,439 --> 00:02:53,120
We'll do it your way.

30
00:03:02,280 --> 00:03:03,879
You should head to the palace.

31
00:03:04,120 --> 00:03:05,599
State matters are waiting for you.

32
00:03:05,960 --> 00:03:06,639
I'm off then.

33
00:03:07,400 --> 00:03:08,400
I'll wait for your message.

34
00:03:26,919 --> 00:03:28,120
Nannies, what are you…

35
00:03:30,240 --> 00:03:31,680
Apa yang sedang kamu lakukan?

36
00:03:31,919 --> 00:03:33,080
You little brat,

37
00:03:33,400 --> 00:03:34,400
always running your mouth!

38
00:03:34,439 --> 00:03:35,199
Gonna send you somewhere
that'll teach you a lesson!

39
00:03:36,120 --> 00:03:36,639
Hold it.
Move!

40
00:03:37,840 --> 00:03:38,800
What's all this?

41
00:03:38,800 --> 00:03:40,439
Miss Qingpu, save me!

42
00:03:40,439 --> 00:03:41,159
Behave yourself!

43
00:03:41,599 --> 00:03:42,599
What a coincidence.

44
00:03:43,240 --> 00:03:44,120
I wanted to tie her up too.

45
00:03:44,520 --> 00:03:45,159
How about

46
00:03:45,159 --> 00:03:46,240
you hand her over to me?

47
00:03:48,639 --> 00:03:49,280
Mother!

48
00:03:51,199 --> 00:03:51,919
Ibu.

49
00:03:54,240 --> 00:03:55,439
I heard everything.

50
00:03:55,680 --> 00:03:57,039
Sorry for troubling you.

51
00:03:57,680 --> 00:03:58,439
Lian!

52
00:03:58,439 --> 00:03:59,680
Ibu.

53
00:03:59,879 --> 00:04:01,520
Why would you do this?

54
00:04:02,479 --> 00:04:04,400
Mother, I was just mad at her.

55
00:04:04,439 --> 00:04:05,280
Why should she

56
00:04:05,280 --> 00:04:07,360
steal my savings

57
00:04:07,719 --> 00:04:08,360
and still expect me

58
00:04:08,360 --> 00:04:10,240
to cover up her scandal?

59
00:04:10,400 --> 00:04:11,400
Why should I?

60
00:04:11,400 --> 00:04:12,560
Her scandal?

61
00:04:13,599 --> 00:04:15,080
That's Chen Yanyun!

62
00:04:15,759 --> 00:04:17,319
But didn't you tell me

63
00:04:18,319 --> 00:04:19,160
that Chen Yanyun

64
00:04:19,160 --> 00:04:21,000
just keeps her as a mistress?

65
00:04:21,079 --> 00:04:22,120
Mistress or not,

66
00:04:22,600 --> 00:04:23,360
she's still

67
00:04:23,360 --> 00:04:24,680
his woman!

68
00:04:25,240 --> 00:04:26,279
If Chen Yanyun hears

69
00:04:26,519 --> 00:04:28,199
you've been spreading rumors

70
00:04:28,600 --> 00:04:30,040
about her and another man,

71
00:04:30,639 --> 00:04:32,120
he'll never let it slide.

72
00:04:35,560 --> 00:04:36,680
Lalu kenapa?

73
00:04:37,279 --> 00:04:38,959
Chen Yanyun may be powerful,

74
00:04:39,079 --> 00:04:39,959
but can he really meddle

75
00:04:39,959 --> 00:04:41,279
in our family business?

76
00:04:42,519 --> 00:04:44,519
I'm gonna get back at Gu Jinzhao!

77
00:04:45,519 --> 00:04:47,240
So what if she has Chen Yanyun?

78
00:04:47,920 --> 00:04:49,240
I still have Wenxiu,

79
00:04:49,560 --> 00:04:50,600
and the Yao family!

80
00:04:51,079 --> 00:04:51,959
I'm not scared of her!

81
00:04:51,959 --> 00:04:53,560
Compared to Chen Yanyun,

82
00:04:53,720 --> 00:04:55,120
the Yao family means nothing!

83
00:04:56,160 --> 00:04:57,800
If you keep causing trouble outside,

84
00:04:58,079 --> 00:04:59,399
you'll get your father killed someday

85
00:04:59,560 --> 00:05:01,040
and bring disaster to our whole Gu family!

86
00:05:01,600 --> 00:05:02,839
Please calm down, Mother.

87
00:05:05,319 --> 00:05:06,079
Ibu,

88
00:05:06,759 --> 00:05:07,759
Lian was really

89
00:05:07,920 --> 00:05:09,399
reckless this time.

90
00:05:09,920 --> 00:05:12,079
But it's not that serious, is it?

91
00:05:12,839 --> 00:05:13,800
At worst,

92
00:05:14,079 --> 00:05:15,800
we apologize in private

93
00:05:15,800 --> 00:05:16,839
and let it go.

94
00:05:17,439 --> 00:05:18,720
If this really gets exposed,

95
00:05:19,160 --> 00:05:19,959
even Chen Yanyun

96
00:05:19,959 --> 00:05:21,959
would lose face.

97
00:05:22,040 --> 00:05:23,279
Apa yang kamu ketahui?

98
00:05:25,959 --> 00:05:27,079
Deyuan's career

99
00:05:27,560 --> 00:05:29,120
will be ruined by you sooner or later!

100
00:05:46,199 --> 00:05:47,600
Ma'am!

101
00:05:47,879 --> 00:05:48,480
It's bad!

102
00:05:48,920 --> 00:05:50,000
Tang wasn't sent away and

103
00:05:50,000 --> 00:05:51,439
Ms. Jinzhao got her.

104
00:05:53,519 --> 00:05:54,600
Ms. Jinzhao is here!

105
00:05:58,639 --> 00:06:00,160
Grandmother, Auntie.

106
00:06:01,639 --> 00:06:02,680
Lian is here too.

107
00:06:03,040 --> 00:06:04,199
Seems everyone's here,

108
00:06:04,199 --> 00:06:05,720
saved me the trouble of going around.

109
00:06:09,399 --> 00:06:10,959
No need for that tone.

110
00:06:11,959 --> 00:06:13,279
I know you've been wronged.

111
00:06:13,959 --> 00:06:14,680
I've heard

112
00:06:14,800 --> 00:06:15,759
about the rumors too.

113
00:06:16,920 --> 00:06:18,720
Your Auntie has been
investigating all day.

114
00:06:19,680 --> 00:06:20,519
We've figured it out now.

115
00:06:21,560 --> 00:06:23,079
It was Tang who spread them.

116
00:06:24,399 --> 00:06:25,519
I was just about to send someone

117
00:06:25,959 --> 00:06:26,720
to arrest her.

118
00:06:27,920 --> 00:06:29,399
We were thinking the same thing.

119
00:06:30,759 --> 00:06:32,680
Grandmother, you're truly wise.

120
00:06:33,240 --> 00:06:34,439
But I think

121
00:06:34,680 --> 00:06:35,759
Tang wouldn't have done it

122
00:06:35,759 --> 00:06:36,600
for no reason.

123
00:06:37,160 --> 00:06:38,439
Someone must have ordered her.

124
00:06:40,879 --> 00:06:42,240
Right, Tang?

125
00:06:43,519 --> 00:06:44,319
Tang,

126
00:06:45,240 --> 00:06:46,759
don't you dare talk nonsense.

127
00:06:52,720 --> 00:06:53,600
Tang,

128
00:06:54,600 --> 00:06:56,279
if Qingpu hadn't arrived in time,

129
00:06:56,879 --> 00:06:57,879
Anda sudah

130
00:06:58,199 --> 00:06:59,920
dikirim ke perkebunan.

131
00:07:07,079 --> 00:07:08,360
Ibu Lian-lah yang menyuruh saya melakukannya.

132
00:07:09,040 --> 00:07:10,360
Dia menyuruhku pergi ke Kuil Baoxiang!

133
00:07:10,360 --> 00:07:12,160
Nyonya Lian yang mengirimmu ke sana.

134
00:07:12,399 --> 00:07:13,800
berdoa untuk

135
00:07:13,800 --> 00:07:15,079
gelang yang disucikan,

136
00:07:15,439 --> 00:07:17,000
jangan menyebarkan omong kosong di sini

137
00:07:17,360 --> 00:07:18,959
dan merusak reputasinya!

138
00:07:19,959 --> 00:07:20,879
Tepat!

139
00:07:21,079 --> 00:07:22,680
Aku tidak pernah menyuruhmu menyebarkan rumor!

140
00:07:23,279 --> 00:07:23,839
Merindukan,

141
00:07:24,000 --> 00:07:25,560
Kaulah yang mengirimku!

142
00:07:26,160 --> 00:07:27,600
Seandainya kau tidak mengajariku,

143
00:07:27,680 --> 00:07:29,000
Bagaimana mungkin aku pernah mengatakan hal-hal itu?

144
00:07:29,000 --> 00:07:29,439
Anda…

145
00:07:31,600 --> 00:07:33,000
Jangan berani-beraninya kau memutarbalikkan kebenaran!

146
00:07:33,399 --> 00:07:34,040
Ibu.

147
00:07:34,639 --> 00:07:35,120
Nama Pengasuh.
Ya!

148
00:07:35,519 --> 00:07:36,319
Tampar dia!
Ya!

149
00:07:43,519 --> 00:07:44,199
Nona Jinzhao,

150
00:07:44,639 --> 00:07:45,439
Ternyata memang Bu Lian yang menyuruh saya
menyebarkan rumor.

151
00:07:46,079 --> 00:07:47,399
tentang Anda dan Tuan Wang!

152
00:07:47,879 --> 00:07:48,560
Dan,

153
00:07:48,759 --> 00:07:50,279
Dia secara khusus menyuruhku
pergi ke Kuil Baoxiang,

154
00:07:50,439 --> 00:07:51,959
mengatakan bahwa aku harus menyebarkannya
di antara para pelayan.

155
00:07:52,079 --> 00:07:53,519
karena banyak wanita bangsawan pergi ke sana untuk berdoa!

156
00:07:53,680 --> 00:07:54,120
Itu adalah

157
00:07:54,120 --> 00:07:55,279
Semua pesanan dari Ibu Lian!

158
00:07:55,759 --> 00:07:57,160
Aku tidak!

159
00:07:57,360 --> 00:07:58,720
Aku tidak!

160
00:07:58,959 --> 00:07:59,519
Nenek.
Cukup!

161
00:08:01,279 --> 00:08:01,959
Bau

162
00:08:02,439 --> 00:08:03,199
awalnya

163
00:08:03,199 --> 00:08:04,920
Pelayan pribadi Lian.

164
00:08:05,439 --> 00:08:07,040
Karena kamu sendiri yang menyebarkan rumor.

165
00:08:07,319 --> 00:08:08,279
dan menuduh Nona Anda secara salah…

166
00:08:09,600 --> 00:08:10,720
Suruh dia dicambuk 20 kali,

167
00:08:11,240 --> 00:08:12,560
lalu kirim dia ke perkebunan itu,

168
00:08:12,879 --> 00:08:14,240
Jangan pernah izinkan dia kembali ke ibu kota!

169
00:08:15,519 --> 00:08:16,319
Nenek,

170
00:08:17,519 --> 00:08:18,639
Tang pantas dihukum,

171
00:08:18,879 --> 00:08:20,240
apa pun itu.

172
00:08:20,600 --> 00:08:21,480
Tapi jangan lupa,

173
00:08:22,120 --> 00:08:23,720
Orang di balik semua ini adalah Lian.

174
00:08:23,959 --> 00:08:24,879
Jangan menunjukkan pilih kasih.

175
00:08:26,360 --> 00:08:27,399
Mengapa kamu begitu cemas?

176
00:08:28,120 --> 00:08:29,920
Siapa bilang aku melindungi Lian?

177
00:08:31,639 --> 00:08:32,519
Lian

178
00:08:32,759 --> 00:08:33,799
gagal mendisiplinkan para pelayannya

179
00:08:34,000 --> 00:08:35,320
dan biarkan seorang selir menderita.

180
00:08:35,759 --> 00:08:36,440
Dia juga harus dihukum.

181
00:08:37,120 --> 00:08:38,240
20 tamparan di telapak tangan,

182
00:08:39,960 --> 00:08:40,840
dan berlutut selama tiga hari

183
00:08:41,159 --> 00:08:42,039
di aula leluhur.

184
00:08:42,159 --> 00:08:43,360
Nenek…

185
00:08:44,639 --> 00:08:45,399
Apa?

186
00:08:46,200 --> 00:08:47,080
Itu terlalu ringan!

187
00:08:47,759 --> 00:08:48,919
Gu Jinzhao, dengarkan.

188
00:08:49,080 --> 00:08:49,960
Jangan coba-coba!

189
00:08:50,559 --> 00:08:52,000
Lian tahu dia salah.

190
00:08:52,519 --> 00:08:53,360
Terima kasih, Ibu.
Kami menerima hukuman ini.

191
00:08:54,279 --> 00:08:55,000
Ayo pergi.
Kami akan menerima hukuman kami!

192
00:08:56,440 --> 00:08:57,600
Kami tahu kami salah!

193
00:08:57,840 --> 00:08:58,519
Nama Pengasuh.

194
00:08:59,080 --> 00:09:00,519
Seret perempuan itu keluar sekarang juga!

195
00:09:00,600 --> 00:09:01,639
Oke. Ada seseorang di sini!

196
00:09:01,879 --> 00:09:02,840
Seret dia keluar!

197
00:09:03,039 --> 00:09:03,759
Bu!

198
00:09:04,039 --> 00:09:05,440
Bu, saya tidak bersalah!

199
00:09:05,559 --> 00:09:05,919
Bergerak!

200
00:09:05,919 --> 00:09:07,679
Istriku menyuruhku melakukan semuanya!

201
00:09:07,799 --> 00:09:09,159
- Aku tidak bersalah!
- Minggir!

202
00:09:09,639 --> 00:09:10,720
Bu!

203
00:09:10,720 --> 00:09:11,559
Kalian semua keluar.

204
00:09:12,879 --> 00:09:13,679
Jinzhao, diamlah.

205
00:09:13,960 --> 00:09:14,519
Ya.

206
00:09:14,960 --> 00:09:16,519
Qingpu, kamu juga ikut.

207
00:09:17,399 --> 00:09:17,919
Ya.

208
00:09:21,799 --> 00:09:22,720
Nenek,

209
00:09:23,600 --> 00:09:24,960
Apa yang sedang kamu coba lakukan?

210
00:09:30,159 --> 00:09:31,000
Jinzhao,

211
00:09:32,200 --> 00:09:33,399
Jangan menatapku seperti itu.

212
00:09:35,679 --> 00:09:36,600
Mengenai hal ini,

213
00:09:36,840 --> 00:09:38,000
Tentu saja aku tahu

214
00:09:39,039 --> 00:09:40,279
Ini semua kesalahan Lian.

215
00:09:45,519 --> 00:09:46,519
Tapi bibimu

216
00:09:47,519 --> 00:09:48,279
hanya punya satu

217
00:09:48,440 --> 00:09:50,240
anak perempuan sah.

218
00:09:50,600 --> 00:09:52,440
Kita tidak bisa begitu saja mengusirnya!

219
00:09:54,519 --> 00:09:55,879
Terus terang saja,

220
00:09:57,039 --> 00:09:59,200
Reputasimu sudah hancur.

221
00:09:59,399 --> 00:10:00,759
Tapi jika nama Lian

222
00:10:00,840 --> 00:10:01,799
ikut rusak juga…

223
00:10:02,559 --> 00:10:03,679
Kemudian keluarga Gu kami,

224
00:10:04,440 --> 00:10:06,120
Hui, Lan,

225
00:10:06,519 --> 00:10:08,080
Jinrong, Jinxian

226
00:10:08,279 --> 00:10:09,039
Apa yang akan mereka lakukan?

227
00:10:09,519 --> 00:10:10,799
Bagaimana mereka bisa menikah?

228
00:10:11,200 --> 00:10:12,200
Bagaimana mereka akan hidup?

229
00:10:14,159 --> 00:10:16,000
Jadi prioritas utama sekarang

230
00:10:18,480 --> 00:10:20,159
bukanlah hukuman,

231
00:10:20,440 --> 00:10:21,960
Tapi bagaimana cara memperbaikinya!

232
00:10:23,879 --> 00:10:26,159
Sepertinya
Nenek sudah punya rencana.

233
00:10:27,480 --> 00:10:28,440
Jangan berpikir

234
00:10:29,320 --> 00:10:30,080
apa yang kamu lakukan

235
00:10:30,519 --> 00:10:32,440
Malam itu, diam-diam pergi ke Kediaman Cuizhu,

236
00:10:32,440 --> 00:10:33,279
tidak diperhatikan.

237
00:10:35,279 --> 00:10:36,159
Kamu sebenarnya tidak berpikir

238
00:10:36,399 --> 00:10:38,240
Kamu bisa menikahi Chen Yanyun, kan?

239
00:10:41,879 --> 00:10:43,679
Kamu terlalu banyak berpikir.

240
00:10:46,200 --> 00:10:46,960
Jika Chen Yanyun

241
00:10:47,679 --> 00:10:49,039
Aku sangat ingin menikahimu,

242
00:10:50,039 --> 00:10:50,600
mengapa dia

243
00:10:50,600 --> 00:10:51,960
bertemu denganmu secara rahasia,

244
00:10:52,120 --> 00:10:53,519
alih-alih secara terbuka

245
00:10:53,519 --> 00:10:54,759
Apakah Anda datang untuk melamar?

246
00:10:56,120 --> 00:10:56,960
Jelas sekali,

247
00:10:57,159 --> 00:10:57,879
dia hanya memperlakukanmu

248
00:10:57,879 --> 00:10:59,320
seperti wanita di luar.

249
00:11:01,759 --> 00:11:02,360
Aku tahu.

250
00:11:03,000 --> 00:11:04,000
Kamu tidak peduli
dengan reputasimu.

251
00:11:05,399 --> 00:11:06,679
Namun putri-putri dari keluarga Gu

252
00:11:07,639 --> 00:11:09,120
tidak bisa menjadi wanita simpanan seseorang!

253
00:11:10,600 --> 00:11:11,960
Jadi satu-satunya cara sekarang

254
00:11:12,320 --> 00:11:13,519
adalah agar kamu menikahi Wang Zan

255
00:11:13,840 --> 00:11:14,840
dan menjaga agar semuanya tetap damai.

256
00:11:29,159 --> 00:11:31,000
Lian menyebarkan desas-desus tentang aku dan Wang Zan.

257
00:11:31,440 --> 00:11:32,720
Jadi, Nenek, solusinya adalah...

258
00:11:32,879 --> 00:11:33,879
untuk menikahkan aku?

259
00:11:35,840 --> 00:11:36,879
Sepertinya

260
00:11:37,080 --> 00:11:38,799
Anda sangat menghargai Wang Zan.

261
00:11:44,360 --> 00:11:45,279
Pernikahan selalu,

262
00:11:45,519 --> 00:11:46,240
sejak zaman kuno,

263
00:11:46,240 --> 00:11:47,519
telah diatur oleh orang tua seseorang.

264
00:11:48,240 --> 00:11:50,159
Saya tidak di sini untuk membahasnya dengan Anda.

265
00:11:52,080 --> 00:11:53,200
Aku juga tidak akan membahasnya denganmu.

266
00:11:53,679 --> 00:11:54,639
Aku tidak akan menikah dengannya.

267
00:11:55,159 --> 00:11:56,440
Sebaiknya kamu lupakan ide ini.

268
00:11:56,639 --> 00:11:57,440
Sungguh keterlaluan!

269
00:11:58,200 --> 00:11:58,879
Siapa yang mengizinkanmu?

270
00:11:58,879 --> 00:12:00,320
Berbicara kepada orang yang lebih tua seperti itu?

271
00:12:13,799 --> 00:12:15,240
Aku mendengar semuanya

272
00:12:15,519 --> 00:12:16,600
Anda mengatakan itu kepada Paman Deyuan.

273
00:12:17,039 --> 00:12:18,039
Apakah kamu tidak takut?

274
00:12:18,360 --> 00:12:19,360
bahwa dengan memaksa saya seperti ini,

275
00:12:19,600 --> 00:12:20,679
setelah saya menikah dan menjadi anggota keluarga Wang,

276
00:12:20,840 --> 00:12:21,879
Aku akan mengungkapkan semuanya

277
00:12:21,879 --> 00:12:22,960
Seharusnya aku tidak?

278
00:12:25,039 --> 00:12:26,720
Itu adalah
kediaman Menteri Kehakiman!

279
00:12:27,039 --> 00:12:28,159
menurut mu

280
00:12:29,000 --> 00:12:30,360
bahwa saat ini di keluarga Gu,

281
00:12:30,960 --> 00:12:32,639
Tidak ada seorang pun yang bisa melakukan apa pun padamu?

282
00:12:33,320 --> 00:12:33,879
Ada seseorang di sini!

283
00:12:34,759 --> 00:12:35,440
Ya!

284
00:12:36,600 --> 00:12:37,600
Kurung dia di gudang kayu,

285
00:12:37,879 --> 00:12:38,600
Tanpa surat perintah saya,
dia tidak diizinkan keluar!

286
00:12:39,440 --> 00:12:39,960
Ya!

287
00:12:40,600 --> 00:12:41,679
Siapa yang berani!

288
00:13:32,360 --> 00:13:33,200
Bu.

289
00:13:33,799 --> 00:13:35,039
Tuan Ji telah tiba.

290
00:13:35,559 --> 00:13:37,320
Dan dia membawa lebih
dari sepuluh gerobak berisi hadiah,

291
00:13:37,559 --> 00:13:38,919
mengatakan bahwa dia datang untuk melamar.

292
00:13:39,639 --> 00:13:40,279
Dia ingin

293
00:13:40,679 --> 00:13:42,080
untuk menikah dengan Nona Jinzhao.

294
00:13:44,080 --> 00:13:45,399
Bukankah itu hanya lamaran pernikahan?

295
00:13:45,840 --> 00:13:46,960
Apa masalahnya?

296
00:13:47,679 --> 00:13:49,000
Jadi jika seseorang datang untuk melamar,

297
00:13:49,360 --> 00:13:50,840
Apakah saya tidak bisa menghukum cucu perempuan saya?

298
00:13:51,720 --> 00:13:52,320
Lakukanlah.

299
00:13:53,919 --> 00:13:54,759
Bu,

300
00:13:55,360 --> 00:13:57,159
Keluarga Ji melayani keluarga Chen.

301
00:14:03,000 --> 00:14:03,639
Baiklah.

302
00:14:04,840 --> 00:14:06,799
Suruh Pak Ji menunggu di aula depan.

303
00:14:07,879 --> 00:14:08,639
Saya akan pergi sekarang.

304
00:14:09,120 --> 00:14:09,639
Ya.

305
00:14:13,080 --> 00:14:14,360
Apakah Deyuan dan Dezhao sudah kembali?

306
00:14:15,240 --> 00:14:16,360
Hanya Master Dezhao yang sedang tidak bertugas,

307
00:14:16,360 --> 00:14:17,279
Dia baru saja kembali.

308
00:14:18,320 --> 00:14:19,159
Suruh dia ikut juga.
Ya.

309
00:14:21,759 --> 00:14:22,879
Pergi cepat!

310
00:14:31,000 --> 00:14:31,879
Anda menelepon

311
00:14:32,039 --> 00:14:32,960
Pak Ji di sini, kan?

312
00:14:33,559 --> 00:14:34,279
TIDAK.

313
00:14:35,360 --> 00:14:36,919
Lalu, apakah itu Chen Yanyun?

314
00:14:37,440 --> 00:14:38,399
Tentu saja tidak!

315
00:14:43,960 --> 00:14:44,600
Merindukan.

316
00:14:46,320 --> 00:14:47,799
Sebenarnya, Tuan Ji datang untuk melamar Anda.

317
00:14:48,399 --> 00:14:49,519
Aku tidak tahu apa yang sedang terjadi.

318
00:14:49,759 --> 00:14:50,080
Ayo pergi

319
00:14:50,120 --> 00:14:51,200
Ke belakang dan lihatlah.

320
00:14:52,559 --> 00:14:53,960
Salam hormat, Nyonya,

321
00:14:54,120 --> 00:14:55,799
Nyonya Kedua, Tuan Keempat.

322
00:15:00,360 --> 00:15:01,200
Tuan Ji,

323
00:15:02,559 --> 00:15:04,159
Apakah kamu ingin menikahi Jinzhao?

324
00:15:04,639 --> 00:15:05,200
Ya.

325
00:15:06,919 --> 00:15:07,879
Nenekku

326
00:15:07,879 --> 00:15:09,120
menyiapkan sendiri hadiah pertunangan tersebut.

327
00:15:09,399 --> 00:15:10,279
Nyonya,
dan Tuan Keempat, mohon periksa kembali.

328
00:15:26,799 --> 00:15:27,799
2000 tael emas.

329
00:15:28,120 --> 00:15:29,039
Dan 50.000 tael perak?

330
00:15:33,159 --> 00:15:34,679
Ibu!

331
00:15:43,240 --> 00:15:44,080
Dengan baik,

332
00:15:44,840 --> 00:15:45,799
Kita bisa bicara.

333
00:15:47,600 --> 00:15:49,000
Saya juga sudah menyiapkan beberapa hadiah kecil.

334
00:15:49,559 --> 00:15:50,639
untuk semua orang tua.

335
00:15:50,960 --> 00:15:51,759
Silakan terima.

336
00:15:58,679 --> 00:15:59,240
Nyonya,

337
00:16:00,159 --> 00:16:01,759
Aku mendapatkan gelang giok ini

338
00:16:01,759 --> 00:16:03,200
dalam perjalanan pengangkutan biji-bijian ke Toungoo.

339
00:16:03,519 --> 00:16:04,360
Kenakan di pergelangan tanganmu,

340
00:16:04,799 --> 00:16:05,799
dan tetap hangat di musim dingin
dan sejuk di musim panas.

341
00:16:14,799 --> 00:16:15,559
Tuan Ji,

342
00:16:16,559 --> 00:16:17,720
Kamu sudah menghabiskan terlalu banyak uang.

343
00:16:19,039 --> 00:16:19,879
Datang dari tempat yang sangat jauh

344
00:16:20,000 --> 00:16:21,200
Pasti sulit.

345
00:16:21,919 --> 00:16:22,600
Demi kata-kataku.

346
00:16:24,519 --> 00:16:25,080
Bu.

347
00:16:25,519 --> 00:16:27,440
Bantulah Pak Ji saat beliau mencuci piring,

348
00:16:27,679 --> 00:16:28,360
Dan,

349
00:16:28,559 --> 00:16:29,919
lalu mengantarnya
ke aula utama untuk makan malam.

350
00:16:31,360 --> 00:16:31,840
Ya.

351
00:16:33,559 --> 00:16:34,360
Terima kasih, Bu.

352
00:16:35,759 --> 00:16:36,399
Tuan Ji,

353
00:16:36,879 --> 00:16:37,440
Tolong.

354
00:16:48,159 --> 00:16:48,720
Apa?

355
00:16:49,320 --> 00:16:50,840
Kau berani datang melamar,

356
00:16:50,960 --> 00:16:51,879
tapi tidak berani menemuiku?

357
00:16:54,159 --> 00:16:55,240
Tidak seperti kamu,

358
00:16:55,559 --> 00:16:56,679
tidak ada rasa malu sama sekali,

359
00:16:56,879 --> 00:16:58,000
dan kamu bahkan tidak melindungi dirimu sendiri.

360
00:16:58,960 --> 00:17:00,320
Kamu telah membuat keributan besar,

361
00:17:00,879 --> 00:17:01,679
membuat Nenek

362
00:17:01,679 --> 00:17:02,840
Sulit tidur berhari-hari.

363
00:17:03,919 --> 00:17:04,640
Apa?

364
00:17:05,640 --> 00:17:07,119
Apakah nenek dari pihak ibu yang mengirimmu?

365
00:17:07,480 --> 00:17:08,039
TIDAK.

366
00:17:08,920 --> 00:17:09,799
Nenek tidak menyebutkannya.

367
00:17:11,240 --> 00:17:12,519
Saya datang sendirian.

368
00:17:14,599 --> 00:17:15,359
Aku mendengar
desas-desus kotor itu.

369
00:17:17,680 --> 00:17:18,720
Itu semua hanya rumor.

370
00:17:19,079 --> 00:17:20,559
Saya tahu itu hanya rumor.

371
00:17:21,079 --> 00:17:22,279
Namun, gosip adalah senjata yang mematikan.

372
00:17:23,200 --> 00:17:24,359
Bahkan seorang pria pun tidak bisa menanganinya,

373
00:17:24,799 --> 00:17:26,200
apalagi seorang wanita muda sepertimu.

374
00:17:26,839 --> 00:17:28,240
Aku benar-benar tidak tahan dengan mereka.

375
00:17:28,240 --> 00:17:29,480
Menyebarkan omong kosong dan merusak nama baikmu.

376
00:17:29,920 --> 00:17:31,720
Tapi kamu tidak perlu melamar!

377
00:17:32,160 --> 00:17:34,240
Mengajukan proposal adalah solusi terbaik.

378
00:17:35,319 --> 00:17:36,039
Saya menyelidikinya.

379
00:17:36,559 --> 00:17:37,319
Wang Zan itu

380
00:17:37,599 --> 00:17:38,839
adalah seorang penjahat terkenal.

381
00:17:39,319 --> 00:17:40,200
Siapa tahu?

382
00:17:40,200 --> 00:17:41,559
Masalah apa yang akan dia timbulkan di masa depan?

383
00:17:42,279 --> 00:17:43,920
Alih-alih berjaga-jaga terhadap rumor,

384
00:17:44,160 --> 00:17:44,720
Saya ingin

385
00:17:44,920 --> 00:17:46,319
untuk melamar Anda sekarang.

386
00:17:46,920 --> 00:17:48,480
Jika ada yang berani mengganggumu nanti,

387
00:17:48,880 --> 00:17:50,000
Saya akan memiliki hak penuh.

388
00:17:50,000 --> 00:17:50,799
untuk menghadapi mereka!

389
00:17:52,039 --> 00:17:52,680
Nona Gu,

390
00:17:54,440 --> 00:17:55,839
Tuan Ji tiba di ibu kota
kemarin siang.

391
00:17:56,079 --> 00:17:57,240
Dia seharusnya bertemu dengan para tamu.

392
00:17:57,960 --> 00:17:58,960
Tapi kemudian dia mendengar

393
00:17:59,079 --> 00:18:00,200
Kamu sedang diintimidasi.

394
00:18:00,359 --> 00:18:01,279
Dia sangat cemas,

395
00:18:01,440 --> 00:18:02,440
membatalkan semua janji temuannya

396
00:18:02,599 --> 00:18:03,920
dan segera kembali
ke Tongzhou untuk bersiap-siap.

397
00:18:04,519 --> 00:18:05,400
Nyonya Ji memberitahunya

398
00:18:05,440 --> 00:18:06,920
menunggu beberapa hari
karena cuaca buruk.

399
00:18:07,319 --> 00:18:08,160
Tapi dia tidak bisa menunggu.

400
00:18:08,640 --> 00:18:10,240
dan tetap datang hari ini.

401
00:18:10,759 --> 00:18:11,960
Aku hanya khawatir kamu akan diperlakukan tidak adil.

402
00:18:12,319 --> 00:18:14,079
Dia bahkan tidak sempat minum seteguk air pun,

403
00:18:14,680 --> 00:18:16,279
dan muncul sariawan di mulut akibat kecemasan.

404
00:18:16,720 --> 00:18:17,400
Cukup,

405
00:18:17,960 --> 00:18:18,799
Kamu terlalu banyak bicara.

406
00:18:20,079 --> 00:18:21,079
Mari datang ke halaman rumahku.

407
00:18:21,720 --> 00:18:22,960
Aku akan membuatkanmu sup biji teratai.

408
00:18:23,240 --> 00:18:24,039
Bagaimana mungkin itu terjadi?

409
00:18:24,519 --> 00:18:25,880
Aku sudah melamar,

410
00:18:26,599 --> 00:18:28,079
Pertemuan seperti ini sudah cukup tidak pantas.

411
00:18:28,079 --> 00:18:29,519
Bagaimana mungkin saya bisa pergi ke halaman Anda?

412
00:18:31,799 --> 00:18:33,200
Kamu, kembalilah sekarang juga,

413
00:18:33,599 --> 00:18:34,519
Jangan khawatir
tentang apa pun,

414
00:18:35,759 --> 00:18:37,160
Serahkan semuanya padaku.

415
00:18:39,559 --> 00:18:40,519
Kalian semua kembali saja.

416
00:18:41,920 --> 00:18:42,400
Ya.

417
00:18:46,279 --> 00:18:47,720
Bagaimana bisa kamu begitu keras kepala?

418
00:18:48,079 --> 00:18:48,559
Ini…
Yao,

419
00:18:51,160 --> 00:18:52,160
Saya sangat tersentuh.

420
00:18:52,640 --> 00:18:53,799
karena apa yang telah kamu lakukan.

421
00:18:55,640 --> 00:18:56,599
Tapi apakah kamu

422
00:18:56,799 --> 00:18:58,000
Apakah dia benar-benar seperti aku?

423
00:19:02,359 --> 00:19:03,039
SAYA…

424
00:19:05,160 --> 00:19:06,559
Tentu saja… aku menyukaimu.

425
00:19:07,680 --> 00:19:08,279
Apakah itu

426
00:19:08,279 --> 00:19:09,759
kasih sayang seorang kakak laki-laki kepada adik perempuannya

427
00:19:10,400 --> 00:19:11,559
atau apakah itu milik seorang pria?

428
00:19:11,839 --> 00:19:13,160
kekaguman pada seorang wanita cantik?

429
00:19:19,680 --> 00:19:21,319
Jika aku menikah dengan seseorang,

430
00:19:21,680 --> 00:19:22,920
itu pasti seseorang

431
00:19:23,000 --> 00:19:23,960
yang benar-benar mencintaiku

432
00:19:24,279 --> 00:19:25,400
dan orang yang sangat saya cintai.

433
00:19:26,200 --> 00:19:26,960
Dan juga,

434
00:19:27,200 --> 00:19:28,759
Sedikit rasa suka saja tidak cukup.

435
00:19:29,079 --> 00:19:30,039
Haruslah yang seperti itu

436
00:19:30,200 --> 00:19:31,200
bahwa ketika saya memikirkannya,

437
00:19:31,559 --> 00:19:33,200
Aku tidak bisa tidur malam demi malam.

438
00:19:34,079 --> 00:19:35,680
Aku akan terus memikirkannya berulang-ulang.

439
00:19:36,839 --> 00:19:38,000
Dan wajahku

440
00:19:38,519 --> 00:19:39,480
bahkan akan menyiram.

441
00:19:39,480 --> 00:19:40,680
Cinta seperti itu.

442
00:19:51,839 --> 00:19:52,599
Milik mereka,

443
00:19:53,440 --> 00:19:55,400
Kami tumbuh bersama.

444
00:19:55,920 --> 00:19:56,799
Saya juga berharap

445
00:19:56,960 --> 00:19:57,920
Anda bisa menemukan seseorang

446
00:19:57,920 --> 00:19:59,079
Kamu benar-benar mencintainya.

447
00:19:59,640 --> 00:20:00,519
Anda menikah,

448
00:20:01,240 --> 00:20:02,079
dan dia menjadi saudara ipar saya.

449
00:20:07,519 --> 00:20:08,680
Sudah larut malam,

450
00:20:09,200 --> 00:20:10,519
Kembali dan istirahatlah lebih awal.

451
00:20:11,160 --> 00:20:12,599
Saya pesan sup biji teratai.

452
00:20:12,759 --> 00:20:14,000
Akan dikirimkan kepada Anda setelah siap.

453
00:20:15,960 --> 00:20:16,720
Saya permisi dulu.

454
00:20:27,039 --> 00:20:28,640
Tidak bisa tidur malam demi malam.

455
00:20:29,640 --> 00:20:31,240
Ia memikirkannya berulang kali.

456
00:20:32,359 --> 00:20:34,400
Dan wajahnya bahkan akan memerah?

457
00:20:37,440 --> 00:20:38,799
Bagaimana dia bisa begitu yakin tentang hal itu?

458
00:20:55,440 --> 00:20:56,039
Pak,

459
00:20:56,599 --> 00:20:57,880
Ada sesuatu yang tidak beres di Gudang Daxin.

460
00:20:58,240 --> 00:20:58,759
Silakan lihat.

461
00:21:09,720 --> 00:21:10,720
Dedak?

462
00:21:13,319 --> 00:21:14,519
Mereka benar-benar bertindak sejauh itu!

463
00:21:15,799 --> 00:21:16,799
Pergilah ke sana sendiri.

464
00:21:17,519 --> 00:21:18,039
TIDAK,

465
00:21:19,599 --> 00:21:20,759
panggil manajer gudang ke sini,

466
00:21:20,920 --> 00:21:21,960
Aku akan menangani ini sendiri.

467
00:21:22,920 --> 00:21:23,400
Ya.

468
00:21:31,119 --> 00:21:32,519
Dulunya tempat ini digunakan untuk menyimpan beras,

469
00:21:32,599 --> 00:21:34,279
Namun, setengah bulan yang lalu,
pakan tersebut diganti dengan dedak.

470
00:21:34,759 --> 00:21:35,720
Mereka berkata, "Dua pagi yang lalu"

471
00:21:36,039 --> 00:21:37,519
Paket itu rencananya akan dikirim ke
Prefektur Pingyang untuk bantuan bencana.

472
00:21:38,039 --> 00:21:39,920
Saya juga merasa ada sesuatu yang tidak beres.

473
00:21:41,119 --> 00:21:42,400
Jelas sekali ada beras di dalam gudang,

474
00:21:42,680 --> 00:21:44,079
Mengapa menggunakan dedak untuk meredakan nyeri?

475
00:21:44,279 --> 00:21:45,440
Tapi aku melihat mereka

476
00:21:45,519 --> 00:21:46,720
Dokumen transportasi semuanya lengkap,

477
00:21:47,039 --> 00:21:47,960
jadi saya tidak mengejarnya.

478
00:21:48,319 --> 00:21:49,519
Siapa yang bertanggung jawab?

479
00:21:49,559 --> 00:21:50,680
dari gudang ini?

480
00:21:50,960 --> 00:21:51,519
Tuanku,

481
00:21:51,680 --> 00:21:53,119
Dia adalah Dewa Sun Shitao.

482
00:21:53,599 --> 00:21:54,680
Sun Shitao?

483
00:21:55,519 --> 00:21:56,119
Pak,

484
00:21:56,799 --> 00:21:57,920
Sun Shitao ini

485
00:21:57,920 --> 00:21:59,599
Dia belum muncul selama beberapa hari.

486
00:22:00,160 --> 00:22:01,640
Lalu dari mana kamu mendapatkan pesanan itu?

487
00:22:01,640 --> 00:22:02,960
untuk biji-bijian yang masuk dan keluar
selama dua hari terakhir?

488
00:22:05,200 --> 00:22:06,359
Tuanku, lihatlah.

489
00:22:50,799 --> 00:22:51,799
Salam, Pak.

490
00:22:52,960 --> 00:22:53,440
Duduk.

491
00:22:54,839 --> 00:22:56,200
Apa yang telah terjadi?

492
00:22:56,960 --> 00:22:58,279
Mengapa Anda membawa Tuan Jiang?

493
00:22:58,519 --> 00:23:00,119
Diam-diam membawaku ke sini?

494
00:23:00,400 --> 00:23:01,079
Jangan khawatir.

495
00:23:02,039 --> 00:23:03,039
Silakan duduk, mari kita bicara perlahan.

496
00:23:07,839 --> 00:23:09,960
Tidak ada seorang pun di rumah yang menyadarinya, kan?

497
00:23:11,200 --> 00:23:12,519
Aku menyuruh Qingpu untuk menontonnya.

498
00:23:12,839 --> 00:23:14,000
Tidak akan ada yang tahu.

499
00:23:19,079 --> 00:23:19,599
Datang,

500
00:23:21,160 --> 00:23:22,160
Minumlah teh,

501
00:23:22,519 --> 00:23:23,240
Ini akan menenangkanmu.

502
00:23:24,279 --> 00:23:25,799
Apakah terjadi sesuatu yang serius?

503
00:23:26,279 --> 00:23:27,039
Jika tidak

504
00:23:27,319 --> 00:23:28,559
Kamu tidak akan memanggilku ke sini.

505
00:23:29,200 --> 00:23:30,359
Sekeras apa pun itu,

506
00:23:30,720 --> 00:23:31,680
Kita tidak seharusnya langsung membahas bisnis
begitu kita bertemu.

507
00:23:33,240 --> 00:23:34,119
Bagaimana bisa begitu?

508
00:23:34,720 --> 00:23:36,240
Apakah ada perbedaan antara berada
di Sekretariat Agung dan di sana?

509
00:23:39,920 --> 00:23:40,680
saya dengar

510
00:23:40,960 --> 00:23:42,240
Ji Yao melamar kamu.

511
00:23:42,880 --> 00:23:43,759
Saya tidak menerimanya.

512
